{"id":3626,"date":"2018-05-03T22:35:43","date_gmt":"2018-05-04T02:35:43","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/?p=3626"},"modified":"2018-06-14T22:16:45","modified_gmt":"2018-06-15T02:16:45","slug":"charitable-classical-piano-concert-to-benefit-ukraines-wounded-soldiers","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/archives\/3626","title":{"rendered":"Charitable Classical Piano Concert to Benefit Ukraine&#8217;s Wounded Soldiers"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"c43i6\" data-offset-key=\"2tj10-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"2tj10-0-0\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3627\" src=\"http:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/31695716_1781545275245927_8119234952639283200_n-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/31695716_1781545275245927_8119234952639283200_n-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/31695716_1781545275245927_8119234952639283200_n-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/31695716_1781545275245927_8119234952639283200_n-285x214.jpg 285w, https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/31695716_1781545275245927_8119234952639283200_n.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/div>\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-offset-key=\"2tj10-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"2tj10-0-0\">The Charitable Concert last Saturday was an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/unitedhelp.art\/posts\/1781545721912549\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">incredible celebration of classical piano music<\/a>. The three musicians took turns at the piano creating a dynamic and beautiful performance. We want to give them another round of applause. Bravo!<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"c43i6\" data-offset-key=\"28h9f-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"28h9f-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"28h9f-0-0\">\u00a0<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"c43i6\" data-offset-key=\"47oca-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"47oca-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"47oca-0-0\">Proceeds from the event, after accounting for expenses, are <strong>$3,074.09<\/strong>. This includes the <strong>$615<\/strong> raised from the ceramics sale of the items donated to us by the <strong>ceramics artists from Michigan<\/strong>. This money will be used to buy the rehabilitation equipment for the <strong>Irpin Military Hospital<\/strong>. A heartfelt thanks to the Michigan artists for donating beautiful ceramics! <\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"c43i6\" data-offset-key=\"d2g27-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"d2g27-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"d2g27-0-0\">\u00a0<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"c43i6\" data-offset-key=\"7a1bi-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"7a1bi-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"7a1bi-0-0\">The rest of the event proceeds, <strong>$2,459<\/strong>, will be used for purchasing a <a href=\"http:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/archives\/3699\">car for double amputee Ukrainian soldier <strong>Ruslan Robert<\/strong><\/a>. With the previously collected<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"c43i6\" data-offset-key=\"1us6s-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-offset-key=\"1us6s-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"1us6s-0-0\">$1,600 via FB fundraiser, $50 check donation and $205 raised in Ukraine, we are now very close to the goal of $6,000 for buying a car for Ruslan and we are very excited about this. So stay tuned for the updates! <\/span